claim.claim-text:
1. A method of preparing a lithographic printing plate, said method comprising: 
providing a lithographic printing plate precursor comprising: 
i) a grained and anodized aluminum substrate comprising an anodic aluminum oxide film wherein the anodic weight of the aluminum oxide film is between 6.0 and 20 g/m2, having coated thereon; 
ii) a metallic layer; 

and image-wise exposing the precursor on an external drum thermal imaging device.
